# Feature: Export Subscription List as CSV

# Overview
We need to implement an export list feature. This will help the user get the list of subscription in csv file format.

# Business Need
User has a lot of subscriptions on the list, we need to implement an export subscription list as csv.

# Requirements
- Add a 'Subcription List' header at the top of the search bar
- Add an export button on the right part of the 'Subsription List', 'Export'+Icon
- Subscription list must be exported in csv file upon clicking the export button